yingyinNormal.en: What do you think? That one. Because of the two additional Ethernet ports? Sure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你觉得呢？那个，因为有两个额外的以太网接口？是的。

yingyinNormal.en: Your heart beats faster, your pupils dilate, and your body releases glucose for additional energy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的心跳加速，瞳孔放大，身体释放出葡萄糖以产生额外的能量。

yingyinNormal.en: New travel measures are now directing all travelers from the three affected countries in West Africa into five U.S. airports where we're conducting additional screening.
yingyinNormal.zh: 新的旅行措施正在指引着所有来自西非三个疫区国家的旅客从美国的五个机场入关，在这五个机场我们正在实施着额外的筛查措施。

yingyinNormal.en: As they divide, these cells may accumulate additional mutations.
yingyinNormal.zh: 随着它们的分裂，这些细胞可能积累诱发更多变异。

yingyinNormal.en: Additional CDC personnel are on the scene in Dallas and Cleveland.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其他的疾控中心人员就在达拉斯和克利夫兰的现场。

yingyinNormal.en: We can install additional devices, but We use what's already there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们可以再加装设备，可是用现成的就行。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh my god. You won't be additional in your life after that, trust me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，我的天啊，在经历了那些之后你不需要把这些带入到你的生活中，相信我。

yingyinNormal.en: But I'm not done. I have many additional concerns about these questions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但我还没说完，我还有更多的关于这些问题的质疑。

yingyinNormal.en: There's absolutely no money in my budget for additional office furniture.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的预算中绝没有添置额外办公家具的那份了。

yingyinNormal.en: For additional freshness, some zingy lime zest, two tablespoons should be about right.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为使菜肴更鲜美，磨一些诱人的青柠末，大约两汤匙即可。

yingyinNormal.en: An Oxford is any formal shoe, with open lacing. This additional decorative piece is called broguing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有鞋带的都可称作牛津鞋，这种有额外装饰的叫做布洛克皮鞋。

yingyinNormal.en: The last thing I want is to be slammed for giving additional money to a brutal dictator from USAID just to persuade him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我最不需要的就是因为从国际开发署拨款给一个我想讨好的残忍独裁者而遭到抨击。

yingyinNormal.en: It would cost billions and billions of dollars to build additional pipeline capacity, and it just doesn't make a lot of sense.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这要花很多很多钱增加管线容量，也没多大意义。

yingyinNormal.en: This original freeway plan promised an additional 1,500 miles of road. And here's what was actually built, just 918 extra miles.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一开始,高速公路计划承诺增加1500英里的道路，而情况却是这样，只有918英里。

yingyinNormal.en: And for men, it was the same, but with one additional caveat: better sleep also led to fewer negative interactions the next day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对男生也是一样的，但却有另个好处：一夜好眠，隔天和另一半互动较好。

yingyinNormal.en: Over the last half-century, the food machine made it cheap and easy for us to put away an average of 600 additional calories per person per day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在过去半个世纪里，食品机器让我们更便宜快捷地 能够额外获得超过600卡的热量，这只是一个人,一天的。

yingyinNormal.en: The additional American forces I've ordered to Iraq will help Iraqi and Kurdish forces with the training, and intelligence and equipment they need to take the fight to these terrorists on the ground.
yingyinNormal.zh: 经我命令派遣到伊拉克的特别武装人员将为伊拉克和库尔德武装提供培训、情报支援和武器装备，支持其开展地面的反恐战争。
